704544f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - Waverly Avenue
704544f-a.text:
Fulton St. adjoining n.e. corner ofWaverly Ave., B'klyn.
May 13, 1942
P.L. Sperr, photographer

707334f-b.title: Brooklyn: Waverly Ave. - Fulton St.
707334f-b.text:
Waverly Avenue, north from near Aulton ftreet, across Gates avenue.
View 2 shows the houses Nos. 467-257 extending to Gates Avenue.
View 3 is north from Gates Avenue.All buildings are on the east
eide of the avenue.
P. L. Sperr  September 28, 1941
